            "code": "# Step 5: After RCMC — full view + range-only x6 crop. Vertical axis is Doppler\n# [Hz], so only the range axis is cropped AND upsampled; Doppler left as-is.\nrg_axis = (t_r - t_r_center) * c / 2\n_W = PEAK_HALF * view_scale\nsurface3d(S_rd_rcmc, rg_axis, f_eta, 'Step 5: After RCMC (full view)', ylabel='Doppler [Hz]')\n_rc = np.where((rg_axis >= -_W) & (rg_axis <= _W))[0]\n_sub = S_rd_rcmc[:, _rc[0]:_rc[-1]+1]\n_rgx = rg_axis[_rc[0]:_rc[-1]+1]\nF = 6\n_mag = upsample_complex_range(_sub, F)\n_rgu = upsample_axis(_rgx, F)\nsurface3d(_mag, _rgu, f_eta, 'Step 5: After RCMC (range x6 crop)', ylabel='Doppler [Hz]', status='upsample x6 (range)')\n",
            "label": "Plot: RCMC",
