            }
          ],
          "defaultParameters": {
            "code": "# LNA (Low Noise Amplifier) — adds receiver thermal noise to the raw echo.\n# Physically the LNA is the front-end stage whose noise figure dominates the\n# receiver noise (Friis), so thermal noise is injected here, right after the\n# antenna/echo. No gain is modelled (the echo path models no attenuation yet),\n# so this stage only ADDS noise; with noise off it is a pass-through.\n#\n# Faithful to sar-visualizer (addComplexGaussianNoise): circular complex\n# Gaussian, sigma = peak / 10^(snrDb/20), split sigma/sqrt(2) per I/Q so the\n# complex-magnitude std equals sigma. snrDb = -noise_level_db (the slider shows\n# noise level: right = more noise). Deterministic via a fixed seed.\nNOISE_SEED = 1\nsnr_db = -float(noise_level_db)            # slider is noise level; SNR is its negation\npeak = float(np.abs(s_raw).max())\nif peak > 0:\n    sigma = peak / (10.0 ** (snr_db / 20.0))\n    sig_comp = sigma / np.sqrt(2.0)\n    rng = np.random.RandomState(int(NOISE_SEED) & 0xFFFFFFFF)\n    noise = (rng.standard_normal(s_raw.shape) + 1j * rng.standard_normal(s_raw.shape)).astype(np.complex64)\n    s_raw = (s_raw + (sig_comp * noise).astype(np.complex64)).astype(np.complex64)\n    print('LNA: noise_level=%.0f dB (SNR=%.0f dB)  sigma=%.3g  peak=%.3g' % (noise_level_db, snr_db, sigma, peak))\nelse:\n    print('LNA: peak=0, no signal -> noise skipped')\n",
            "label": "LNA",
            "spec": "Low Noise Amplifier (receiver front-end). Adds receiver thermal noise to the raw echo here because the LNA's noise figure dominates the system noise (Friis). Noise model matches sar-visualizer: circular complex Gaussian, sigma = peak / 10^(SNR_dB/20), split sigma/sqrt(2) per I/Q. The slider sets noise level (= -SNR_dB); at the -60 dB minimum noise is ~1/1000 of the peak (effectively off). Gain = 1 (no amplification): the echo path models no attenuation yet, so this stage only adds noise and otherwise passes the signal through."
          },
          "executionOrder": 16,
          "codeCollapsed": true
        },
        "width": 400,
        "style": {}
      },
